  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the effectiveness of epoetin alfa in treating anemia
      in patients who have cancer or who no longer have any signs of the cancer, but remain anemic
      as a result of their treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    This study was stopped because of an inadequate rate of enrollment.
  </why_stopped>
